Suite/Test/Step Name: 03 Inden Kerja Cara Bayaran EFT Dengan Pemfaktoran
Test Cases/Perolehan/006 Arahan Bayaran/006 Penyemak Inden Kerja
Description: Penyemak will check the record and click Semak button to verify
open browser and enter ispek URL
login into the system as PROC test

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Perolehan/007 Proses Baucar Bayaran/003 Pelulus Baucar Bayaran IK - EFT
Description: Pelulus will process the baucar bayaran
open browser and enter ispek URL
click on menu sisi to expand menu selection

Suite/Test/Step Name: click(findTestObject("Object Repository/Perolehan/007 Proses Baucar Bayaran/Menu_Akaun Belum Bayar"))
Description: select on sub-menu akaun belum bayar
enter baucar bayaran rekod id into the filter field
double click on the filter result

Suite/Test/Step Name: namapenerima = getText(findTestObject("Perolehan/007 Proses Baucar Bayaran/001 Pelulus IK/Nama_Penerima"))
Description: get the value of Nama Penerima
verify that nama penerima is what is set when filling in dengan pemfaktoran = Ya
get text of amount from the screen
verify that amount is a match
click on button Lulus to approve the record

Suite/Test/Step Name: No_Baucar = getText(findTestObject("Perolehan/007 Proses Baucar Bayaran/div_Rekod Berjaya Diluluskan"))
Description: Get text of No Baucar from the prompt
take only the baucar ID which is from index 40 until 52
set global variable value of Nombor_Baucar with variable Baucar_id
click on Ya button to confirm cetak
switch to second tab to get screenshot of baucar bayaran after select cetak = Ya
wait 180seconds  for the baucar bayaran page to load
switch back the tab to main tab

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Perolehan/008 Posting Bayaran/001 Posting Bayaran - EFT
Description: Posting Bayaran is done in CM to process the baucar with cara bayaran EFT
open chrome browser and input ispek URL
click on drop down no baucar
input no baucar that is saved in global variable
click on the record after it has been filtered. only one record will be displayed based on no baucar entered
check on the checkbox which is located on the end of record
click button proses to process the record
click on Ya to confirm process
wait for 180seconds for the pop-up to display, before verify the posting is successful
click on ok button to close the prompt

Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Perolehan/009 Penyedia Cetak Baucar Bayaran/001 Penyedia Cetak Baucar Bayaran
Description: Penyedia will access AP and cetak baucar bayaran after the posting
Open browser and get to ispek URL
click on menu akaun belum bayar
click on menu carian akaun belum bayar to retrieve the baucar id that is previously processed
click on drop down jenis carian

Suite/Test/Step Name: setText(findTestObject("Perolehan/009 Penyedia Cetak Baucar Bayaran/Input_No_Baucar"), Nombor_Baucar)
Description: input no baucar that is a global variable baucar id
click on button cari to search for the record
click on button cetak to print the baucar again
wait for the page to load the document which will take some times
take the screen shot of the document loaded
switch to window tab index 1 to get the baucar displayed
